        "created_at": "2023-01-13T04:20:39.608Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Hello experts, our clients used volumeClaim to define storageclass in the old apple operator release like 0.48.0, but now we will upgrade to 1.4.1 v1beta2, but found volumeClaim was removed, after upgrade to new 1.4.1 and use volumeClaimTemplate, the old pv was deleted, new pvc was created, that means the old data in pv is lost,how could we ensure data won\u2019t lost after upgrade ? kindly advise. thank you.</p>",
