        "created_at": "2023-01-13T12:58:20.127Z",
        "cooked": "<p>v1beta1 supports <code>volumeClaimTemplates</code> before doing the update to the v1beta2 CRD you should convert all <code>volumeClaim</code> definitions to <code>volumeClaimTemplates</code>.</p>\n<p>See: <a href=\"https://github.com/FoundationDB/fdb-kubernetes-operator/blob/main/api/v1beta1/foundationdbcluster_types.go#L1136\" class=\"inline-onebox\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">fdb-kubernetes-operator/foundationdbcluster_types.go at main \u00b7 FoundationDB/fdb-kubernetes-operator \u00b7 GitHub</a></p>",
